text: Servance-Miellin is a commune. It is in Bourgogne-Franche-Comté in the Haute- Saône department in east France. The municipality was created on 1 January 2017 and consists of the former communes of Servance (the seat) and Miellin.Arrêté préfectoral 26 September 2016 == References == Category:2017 establishments in France Category:Communes in Haute-Saône
title: Servance-Miellin
